Marlon Roudette - When The Beat Drops Out (Matoma Tropical Remix)
description:
The last few months have been amazing in terms of remix assignments and gigs. This remix is an official mission from Universal Germany for the artist Marlon Roudette new hit "When the beat drops out", it climbs the charts throughout Europe and when I heard the original for the first time I understand why. Marlon really has an amazing voice and I have done my best to create a good tune around the solid vocals. hope you will enjoy the remix as much as I did making it!

Photocredit:
Kamilla Paulsen
http://milligramdesign.no/

Like it? Heart it on Hype Machine: http://hypem.com/track/2623z/Marlon+Roudette+-+When+The+Beat+Drops+Out+(Matoma+Tropical+Remix)

description:
Get 300MB of free dub & reggae loops from Dubmatix

Marley's music had an immense impact on me as a youth and still resonates today Like many, he was my first introduction to reggae and since my first listen back in the 70s and 80s to now, his music does and will continue to stand the test of time and impact generations of fans and musicians alike for  the high quality of song writing and his message of harmony and peace.. 

This re-vision of  "Is This Love" was done a few years ago as a free "white label" promo. Please feel free to share.
